{
  "page": "One Eye",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">One Eye</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Elena-maria-vacas-varamyrsixskins.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Elena-maria-vacas-varamyrsixskins.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b9/Elena-maria-vacas-varamyrsixskins.jpg/400px-Elena-maria-vacas-varamyrsixskins.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"241\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b9/Elena-maria-vacas-varamyrsixskins.jpg/600px-Elena-maria-vacas-varamyrsixskins.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b9/Elena-maria-vacas-varamyrsixskins.jpg/800px-Elena-maria-vacas-varamyrsixskins.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Varamyr Sixskins and his animals, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artist/ab3nd\">Elena María Vacas</a></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nHead</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Owner</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Varamyr_Sixskins\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Varamyr Sixskins\">Varamyr Sixskins</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Species</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">Wolf</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>One Eye</b> is a wolf. He is one of the three wolves that <a href=\"/index.php/Varamyr\" title=\"Varamyr\">Varamyr</a> can enter into as a <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">skinchanger</a>, and the head of the pack. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=One_Eye&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>One Eye is the biggest of Varamyr's wolves and the oldest. While <a href=\"/index.php/Stalker\" title=\"Stalker\">Stalker</a> is leaner and quicker, and <a href=\"/index.php/Sly\" title=\"Sly\">Sly</a> more cunning, One Eye is the largest and the fiercest.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> One Eye has grey-brown fur,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> a grizzled white muzzle, and is blind in one eye.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> When Sly goes into heat, One Eye is the wolf that mounts her, not Stalker.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=One_Eye&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=One_Eye&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>One Eye, Stalker, and Sly chase down and kill a party of <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a> for food. Varamyr considers which of his animals he will enter into when he dies, and thinks the younger Stalker might suit him, but prefers One Eye. Varamyr dies, and enters One Eye for his <a href=\"/index.php/Second_life\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Second life\">second life</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Summer\" title=\"Summer\">Summer</a> encounters the wolf pack eating the remains of the dead <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> deserters. Summer sees that One Eye is not afraid of him even though he is twice the wolf's size. He realizes that One Eye has a <a href=\"/index.php/Warg\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Warg\">warg</a> within him, and they fight. After defeating One Eye and making him submit, Summer makes Stalker and Sly submit as well, and takes over leadership of the pack.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Near the <a href=\"/index.php/Cave_of_the_last_greenseer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cave of the last greenseer\">cave of the last greenseer</a>, Summer and the pack find a wight <a href=\"/index.php/Snow_bear\" title=\"Snow bear\">snow bear</a>, and tear it to pieces and devour it, even though the rotten meat still moves while they eat it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=One_Eye&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Prologue\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Prologue\">Prologue</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_4\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 4\">Chapter 4</a>, Bran I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Prologue\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Prologue\">Prologue</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Da